  1.000     p+            pi-                HELAMP 0.9276 0.0 0.3735 0.0;
Enddecay
CDecay MyantiLambda

Decay Mychic2
  0.500     p+  MyantiLambda    K-  PHSP;
  0.500     anti-p-  MyLambda    K+  PHSP;
Enddecay

